We conquered the Muddy Princess Run 🏃‍♂️ in support of the National Breast Cancer Foundation. 🩷 The NBCF aims to fill in the gaps of cancer care. Providing education and support services. 
Next runs are in Temecula, CA on April 30, Michigan on August 6 & 13 & Nashville on September 24. 

🙋‍♀️ if you’ve recently had your mammogram or are scheduled to get yours soon.

🩷 🙏 if you know someone affected by breast cancer.

Two young kids and puppy love.
It started cutting up his film on a steenbeck in ‘98. #happyanniversarytims ✨

Maxden is three!!! 3️⃣ My little man! He is so funny, silly, kind, and snuggly. He loves to play catch but mostly loves to throw (and his aim is ‘spot on’). His favorite color is blue. Except for today, he’s officially changed it to red, you know, because he’s 3 now.  His number one request for food is popcorn, runners up; pepperoni, salami, olives, red bell pepper, and a new favorite, chocolate. Add swimming to his favorites, jumping on the trampoline, of course, and spinning on the hammock.  Little man, theres so much personality in you. You make me laugh every day. I’m one lucky mommy. Happy 3!!!!!!
